Wow those photos from the Aizu Festival were so cool! I have never been able to go to one of the many festivals of Japan or any country and to be ablt to see photos from a festival with the Shinsengumi (albeit only characters) is truly wonderful. Thank you for taking these photos and sharing them with us all.
